13 December 2019 - The scene where Rashied Staggie was shot dead. The aftermath of the flash floods in Mamelodi. Former Hard Livings gang leader, Rashied Staggie, has been shot and killed in Salt River, Cape Town. Flood victims in Mamelodi say they have not received any support from the provincial government. Flood victims in Mamelodi say they have not received any support from the provincial government.